<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3814474>
    dc:description "Figures 32-35. Heterotheridion nigrovariegatum Simon (32-33), male and female from South Tyrol, courtship (32), copulation (33). Theridion genistae Simon (34-35), female from Kephallonia (34), male from Corsica (35)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3814474/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3814476>
    dc:description "Figures 36-40. Theridion genistae Simon from Corfu. Male palp, retrolateral (36), ventral (37), prolateral view (38). Epigynum/vulva, ventral (39), dorsal view (40). 36-38 and 39-40 drawn at same scale. Scale lines: 0.10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3814476/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

